## important modules
- "@google/maps" -> map
- "bcrypt-nodejs" -> encoding password 
- "fast-csv" -> csv import
- "google-distance-matrix" -> calculate distance
- "helmet" -> security
- "html-pdf" -> pdf conversion
- "mongoose" -> mongoDB connection
- "multer" -> file upload
- "nodemailer" -> email service
- "passport" -> signup signin
- "raven" -> error detector
- "snyk" -> dependency check

## models
- customer
  - customer schema
- shop
  - In testing, appointment, order, quote, invoice schemas
  - Everything else
  
## views(EJS templating engine)
- calendar
- customer views
- common headers
- shop views
- template for email
- index, reset, forgot password page
  
## public
- css(css files)
- javascripts(jquery/angularJS script files)
    - js for customer
    - js for signup signin
    - js for shop

## routes(RESTful API)
- customer url
- shop url
- index, reset, forgot password, activate

## functionality
- csv import
- check login status
- decimal number
- global search

## config
- passport strategy for customer and shop
